snippet.title: METAL GEAR SOLID: MASTER COLLECTION Vol. 1 - Nintendo Direct 6.21.2023
snippet.description:
METAL GEAR SOLID: MASTER COLLECTION Vol.1 is coming to Nintendo Switch on October 24, 2023. Pre-order today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/metal-gear-solid-master-collection-vol-1-switch/

METAL GEAR SOLID: MASTER COLLECTION Vol. 1 brings the beginning of the METAL GEAR gameplay experience in one single package for gamers everywhere. Infiltrate enemy fortresses, complete your missions with stealth and experience the thrilling cinematic story of the METAL GEAR series.

#METALGEAR #NintendoSwitch #NintendoDirect
